{"_env":"NODEJS","_serializationMethod":"normal","_autosave":false,"_autosaveInterval":5000,"_collections":[{"name":"items","unindexedSortComparator":"js","defaultLokiOperatorPackage":"js","_dynamicViews":[],"uniqueNames":[],"transforms":{},"rangedIndexes":{},"_data":[{"slug":"about","toc":[],"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"My name is Le Duc Thinh and I'm Vietnamese. Currently, I'm living in Toronto, Canada."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I'm an extrover and optimistic person who loves to hang out with my friends. I have many hobbies - traveling, playing soccer, playing computer games, singing and of course, coding are some of them. Before I went to Canada, I has backpacked to many famous places in Vietnam with my friends using motobike which wasn't allowed by my parents because it's considered dangerous but I managed to sneak out everytime hahaha. Such wonderful memories!"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I am also a talented soccer player! I played for my class and school teams and used to be an agressive player on field until I got ligament injury."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I haven't had many changes to travel since I went to Canada because studying costs me majority of my time and no soccer also. Singing has become my main hobby since then. I sing all day, sometimes I got complained by my landlord because I'm too noisy hahaha. Because of Covid-19, I cannot hang out often anymore so I created a budget karaoke webapp haha, check it in my project section!"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I did participate in 2 start-ups while I was studying in university but both had to stop because of our team's member personal issue but I still managed to learn some valuable experience!"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I want to tell you more about myself but it will take days xD. Just one more thing, I also love playing computer games and I have a group of Vietnamese people who play Dota2 and Among Us. Feel free to poke me if you read this!"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"And check out my other contents!"}]}]},"text":"My name is Le Duc Thinh and I'm Vietnamese. Currently, I'm living in Toronto, Canada.\r\n\r\nI'm an extrover and optimistic person who loves to hang out with my friends. I have many hobbies - traveling, playing soccer, playing computer games, singing and of course, coding are some of them. Before I went to Canada, I has backpacked to many famous places in Vietnam with my friends using motobike which wasn't allowed by my parents because it's considered dangerous but I managed to sneak out everytime hahaha. Such wonderful memories!\r\n\r\nI am also a talented soccer player! I played for my class and school teams and used to be an agressive player on field until I got ligament injury.\r\n\r\nI haven't had many changes to travel since I went to Canada because studying costs me majority of my time and no soccer also. Singing has become my main hobby since then. I sing all day, sometimes I got complained by my landlord because I'm too noisy hahaha. Because of Covid-19, I cannot hang out often anymore so I created a budget karaoke webapp haha, check it in my project section!\r\n\r\nI did participate in 2 start-ups while I was studying in university but both had to stop because of our team's member personal issue but I still managed to learn some valuable experience!\r\n\r\nI want to tell you more about myself but it will take days xD. Just one more thing, I also love playing computer games and I have a group of Vietnamese people who play Dota2 and Among Us. Feel free to poke me if you read this!\r\n\r\nAnd check out my other contents!","dir":"/","path":"/about","extension":".md","createdAt":"2021-03-07T04:25:43.355Z","updatedAt":"2021-03-07T04:25:43.355Z","meta":{"version":0,"revision":0,"created":1615091758017},"$loki":1}],"idIndex":[1],"maxId":1,"_dirty":true,"_nestedProperties":[],"transactional":false,"asyncListeners":false,"disableMeta":false,"disableChangesApi":true,"disableDeltaChangesApi":true,"cloneObjects":false,"cloneMethod":"deep","changes":[],"_fullTextSearch":{"ii":{"title":{"_store":true,"_optimizeChanges":true,"docCount":0,"docStore":[],"totalFieldLength":0,"root":{}},"description":{"_store":true,"_optimizeChanges":true,"docCount":0,"docStore":[],"totalFieldLength":0,"root":{}},"slug":{"_store":true,"_optimizeChanges":true,"docCount":1,"docStore":[[0,{"fieldLength":1}]],"totalFieldLength":1,"root":{"k":[97],"v":[{"k":[98],"v":[{"k":[111],"v":[{"k":[117],"v":[{"k":[116],"v":[{"d":{"df":1,"dc":[[0,1]]}}]}]}]}]}]}},"text":{"_store":true,"_optimizeChanges":true,"docCount":1,"docStore":[[0,{"fieldLength":275}]],"totalFieldLength":275,"root":{"k":[109,110,105,108,100,116,97,118,99,101,111,112,119,104,102,45,115,103,98,117,107,50,121,120,106,114],"v":[{"k":[121,97,111,101],"v":[{"d":{"df":1,"dc":[[0,10]]},"k":[115],"v":[{"k":[101],"v":[{"k":[108],"v":[{"k":[102],"v":[{"d":{"df":1,"dc":[[0,1]]}}]}]}]}]},{"k":[110,106,105],"v":[{"k":[121,97],"v":[{"d":{"df":1,"dc":[[0,3]]}},{"k":[103],"v":[{"k":[101],"v":[{"k":[100],"v":[{"d":{"df":1,"dc":[[0,2]]}}]}]}]}]},{"k":[111],"v":[{"k":[114],"v":[{"k":[105],"v":[{"k":[116],"v":[{"k":[121],"v":[{"d":{"df":1,"dc":[[0,1]]}}]}]}]}]}]},{"k":[110],"v":[{"d":{"df":1,"dc":[[0,1]]}}]}]},{"k":[116,114],"v":[{"k":[111],"v":[{"k":[98],"v":[{"k":[105],"v":[{"k":[107],"v":[{"k":[101],"v":[{"d":{"df":1,"dc":[[0,1]]}}]}]}]}]}]},{"k":[101],"v":[{"d":{"df":1,"dc":[[0,2]]}}]}]},{"d":{"df":1,"dc":[[0,2]]},"k":[109],"v":[{"k":[111,98],"v":[